# Brightness
{_,shift + ,super + }XF86MonBrightness{Down,Up}
    xbacklight {-dec 1,-dec 10,-set 0,-inc 1,-inc 10,-set 100}

alt + Shift_L
    setxkbmap -layout us,cz -variant ,qwerty && xkb-switch -n

